title: The Lauderdale papers.
author: Lauderdale, John Maitland
snippet: Yesternight Longi. told Newbyth that before thelast Council day a friend of his came to him, & with a more thanordinary sadness in his countenance askt him if he meant to keepthe next council day ? He answered he intended it. The otheradvised him not to go ; hee askt why ? The reply was, that forcertain Archb.

title: Domestic details
author: Crossrig, David Hume
snippet: Sir John Baird of Newbyth, created a baronet by K. Chas. II.
